  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underworld</strong> is a classic old-school action role-playing game (ARPG) set in a dark, demonic world full of danger and secrets. Enter a cursed realm where the boundary between life and death has long since been broken, and ancient evils lurk around every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a lone female ninja, you face relentless hordes of demonic skeletons and other nightmarish creatures that haunt the underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your path by collecting powerful runes, upgrading your inventory, improving your gear, and unlocking devastating abilities. As you grow stronger, you’ll discover new combat techniques.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With fast-paced battles and a dark fantasy atmosphere, <i>Underworld</i> delivers an intense ARPG experience for fans of the genre.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underworld</strong> is a classic old-school action role-playing game (ARPG) set in a dark, demonic world full of danger and secrets. Enter a cursed realm where the boundary between life and death has long since been broken, and ancient evils lurk around every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a lone female ninja, you face relentless hordes of demonic skeletons and other nightmarish creatures that haunt the underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your path by collecting powerful runes, upgrading your inventory, improving your gear, and unlocking devastating abilities. As you grow stronger, you’ll discover new combat techniques.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With fast-paced battles and a dark fantasy atmosphere, <i>Underworld</i> delivers an intense ARPG experience for fans of the genre.</p>",
